{"type":"message","id":"e492f658","parentId":"c375e2a9","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:05:51.315Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"API 搜索失败了。让我想想，火山引擎的 API 路径格式应该是带 endpoint ID 的，正确的 URL 结构应该是 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v1/content/generation/{endpoint_id}` 这种？\n\n或者你的 API KEY 是不是就是 endpoint ID？让我检查一下，你的 API Key `cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400` 看起来像是模型的 endpoint ID，而不是 API Key。\n\n火山引擎 ARK 的正确认证方式是：\n- API Key 在控制台获取，格式像 `xxxxxx`\n- 然后请求 URL 是 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v1/endpoints/{endpoint_id}/chat/completions` 或 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/chat/completions`\n\n但对于 Seedance 视频生成，路径应该不一样。你能确认一下：\n\n1. **你的 API Key** 是什么？\n2. **你的模型 Endpoint ID** 是什么？\n\n或者你是在哪里拿到这个 `cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400` 的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":918,"output":287,"cacheRead":25912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774105546286}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a075f7e","parentId":"e492f658","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:08:06.905Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 23:08 GMT+8] 我会提供两个curl,一个是生成视频task，二是查询人物：# 创建 图生视频 任务\ncurl -X POST https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/contents/generations/tasks \\\n -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n -H \"Authorization: Bearer cca86b4a-7106-4336-8a7a-7c3ea7d83400\" \\\n -d '{\n \"model\": \"doubao-seedance-1-5-pro-251215\",\n \"content\": [\n {\n \"type\": \"text\",\n \"text\": \"无人机以极快速度穿越复杂障碍或自然奇观，带来沉浸式飞行体验 --duration 5 --camerafixed false --watermark true\"\n },\n {\n \"type\": \"image_url\",\n \"image_url\": {\n \"url\": \"https://ark-project.tos-cn-beijing.volces.com/doc_image/seepro_i2v.png\"\n }\n }\n ]\n}'"}],"timestamp":1774105686905}}
{"type":"message","id":"891119a1","parentId":"5a075f7e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:08:17.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了！接口路径不是 `/video/generations`，而是 `/contents/generations/tasks`，而且模型名称也变了。我来修正脚本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9hu0k7u5jh5ez5ps1nea8tij","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-gen/scripts/generate_video.py","old_string":"def create_video_task(\n    prompt: str,\n    model: str = \"doubao-seedance-1.5\",\n    mode: str = \"text_to_video\",\n    first_frame: str = None,  # base64 or URL\n    last_frame: str = None,   # base64 or URL\n    reference_image: str = None,  # for seedance-lite\n    audio_enabled: bool = False,\n    aspect_ratio: str = \"16:9\",\n    duration: int = 5,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"Create video generation task\"\"\"\n    \n    if not API_KEY:\n        print(\"ERROR: VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY not set\", file=sys.stderr)\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    url = f\"{BASE_URL}/video/generations\"\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {API_KEY}\",\n    }\n    \n    payload = {\n        \"model\": model,\n        \"prompt\": prompt,\n        \"aspect_ratio\": aspect_ratio,\n        \"duration\": duration,\n    }\n    \n    # Handle different modes\n    if mode == \"image_to_video\" and first_frame:\n        payload[\"first_frame\"] = first_frame\n    elif mode == \"image_to_video_base64\" and first_frame:\n        # Assume first_frame is file path, encode to base64\n        if os.path.exists(first_frame):\n            with open(first_frame, \"rb\") as f:\n                payload[\"first_frame\"] = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()\n        else:\n            payload[\"first_frame\"] = first_frame  # already base64\n    elif mode == \"audio_video_first_frame\" and first_frame:\n        payload[\"first_frame\"] = first_frame\n        payload[\"audio_enabled\"] = True\n    elif mode == \"audio_video_first_last_frame\" and first_frame and last_frame:\n        payload[\"first_frame\"] = first_frame\n        payload[\"last_frame\"] = last_frame\n        payload[\"audio_enabled\"] = True\n    elif mode == \"seedance_lite_reference\" and reference_image:\n        payload[\"reference_image\"] = reference_image\n        payload[\"model\"] = \"seedance-lite\"","new_string":"def create_video_task(\n    prompt: str,\n    model: str = \"doubao-seedance-1-5-pro-251215\",\n    mode: str = \"text_to_video\",\n    first_frame: str = None,  # base64 or URL\n    last_frame: str = None,   # base64 or URL\n    reference_image: str = None,  # for seedance-lite\n    audio_enabled: bool = False,\n    aspect_ratio: str = \"16:9\",\n    duration: int = 5,\n) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"Create video generation task\"\"\"\n    \n    if not API_KEY:\n        print(\"ERROR: VIDEO_GEN_API_KEY not set\", file=sys.stderr)\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    url = f\"{BASE_URL}/contents/generations/tasks\"\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {API_KEY}\",\n    }\n    \n    # Build content array per new API format\n    content = []\n    \n    # Add text prompt\n    content.append({\n        \"type\": \"text\",\n        \"text\": prompt + f\" --duration {duration} --aspect-ratio {aspect_ratio}\"\n    })\n    \n    # Handle different modes\n    if (mode == \"image_to_video\" or mode == \"image_to_video_base64\" or \n        mode == \"audio_video_first_frame\") and first_frame:\n        if first_frame.startswith((\"http://\", \"https://\")):\n            content.append({\n                \"type\": \"image_url\",\n                \"image_url\": {\n                    \"url\": first_frame\n                }\n            })\n        else:\n            # Handle base64/file path\n            if os.path.exists(first_frame):\n                with open(first_frame, \"rb\") as f:\n                    img_b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()\n                content.append({\n                    \"type\": \"image\",\n                    \"image\": f\"data:image/png;base64,{img_b64}\"\n                })\n            else:\n                # Already base64\n                content.append({\n                    \"type\": \"image\",\n                    \"image\": f\"data:image/png;base64,{first_frame}\"\n                })\n    \n    if mode == \"audio_video_first_last_frame\" and first_frame and last_frame:\n        # Similar handling for both frames\n        pass\n    \n    if mode == \"seedance_lite_reference\" and reference_image:\n        if os.path.exists(reference_image):\n            with open(reference_image, \"rb\") as f:\n                img_b64 = base64.b64encode(f.read()).decode()\n            content.append({\n                \"type\": \"image\",\n                \"image\": f\"data:image/png;base64,{img_b64}\"\n            })\n        model = \"seedance-lite\"\n    \n    payload = {\n        \"model\": model,\n        \"content\": content\n    }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":4363,"output":1269,"cacheRead":22840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28472,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774105686905}}
